d state, supporting models where the disk\nis truncated at low luminosities. We find, however, that the lack of\nvariability power on time scales of ~50 sec in the Suzaku low/hard state data\nis difficult to explain, even with a low mass black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Sep 2013 20:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
