al to log(1/(1-eta)). Thus, in the high-loss regime for which eta << 1, this\nnew upper bound demonstrates that the protocols corresponding to the above\nlower bound are nearly optimal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2013 03:01:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2013 10:57:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 04:04:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-16"}
