, the dispersion of excitations is\ndiffusive which as soon as the condensate is put into motion implies finite\nmechanical friction and can lead to an energetic instability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2013 08:23:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Oct 2013 08:54:33 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2014 13:47:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
